release.name: v2.2.0
release.body:
## What's Changed
* Feature/constraint protected delegated#312 by @cspray in https://github.com/cspray/annotated-container/pull/324
* Add check for a service with duplicate names. Fix #311 by @cspray in https://github.com/cspray/annotated-container/pull/325
* Task/improve abstract container factory by @cspray in https://github.com/cspray/annotated-container/pull/327
* Add command to run logical constraint checks by @cspray in https://github.com/cspray/annotated-container/pull/332
* Feature/non public service prepare/313 by @cspray in https://github.com/cspray/annotated-container/pull/335
* Add check for duplicate service types by @cspray in https://github.com/cspray/annotated-container/pull/336
* Allow creating a delegated parameter store factory by @cspray in https://github.com/cspray/annotated-container/pull/337
* Feature/constraint multiple service prepare by @cspray in https://github.com/cspray/annotated-container/pull/338
* Feature/illuminate container v2 by @cspray in https://github.com/cspray/annotated-container/pull/339
* Feature/constraint multiple service delegate by @cspray in https://github.com/cspray/annotated-container/pull/340
* Task/update for 2 2 by @cspray in https://github.com/cspray/annotated-container/pull/341


**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/cspray/annotated-container/compare/v2.1.0...v2.2.0
